gate.corpora.twitter

Class PreAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • gate.corpora.twitter.PreAnnotation

  • public class PreAnnotation
extends Object
    This is a wrapper around the data that we will want to turn into an Annotation later, but here it's a floater, not attached to any Document or AnnotationSet. Used to hold data in the Tweet model.
